description:
These dancers resides on an island among the Orange Archipelago and they beleive strongly that the Meowth of Bounty will visit the island gift give wealth to its followers by using Pay Day.
When Meowth from Team Rocket landed on the island they thought that it was the Meowth of Bounty and made his stay on the island confortable for him by providing entertainment.
name: Meowth of Bounty Dancers
